sql:
SELECT close
FROM market_data
WHERE asset_id = 1 AND time = 1;

external_knowledge:
- "Riding high" refers to having a high closing price; 
- "Decade of days" metaphorically represents a 10-day period; 
- "Recent market waves" refers to the 5-day and 10-day Simple Moving Averages (SMA5 and SMA10).

